        public void createAnimation(java.awt.Point newPosition,
                            java.awt.Dimension tileSize)
        get an array that indicates the number of frames for each status. the default statuses are IDLE = and MOVING = , so an array with 2 Integer is expected, the first one that says the number of frames for IDLE and the 2nd that says the number of frames for MOVING.
